### Financial Performance KPIs

| KPI | How to Track | What Success Looks Like | Key Decision Impact |
|-----|-------------|------------------------|---------------------|
| **AGI (Monthly)** | Automated from accounting system | Predictable growth, <20% variance | Can we hire? Should we invest? |
| **AGI%** | Automated calculation | 80-90%, improving | Should we restructure pricing? |
| **EBITDA Margin** | Monthly P&L, calculate EBITDA | 20-30% sustained | Can we reinvest in systems? |
| **Compensation %** | Payroll ÷ AGI, tracked monthly | ≤45%, controlled | Can we afford next hire? |
| **SG&A %** | Non-payroll costs ÷ AGI | ≤20%, monitored | Where can we cut waste? |
