**Tracking method:**
- Monthly formal P&L review (1-2 hours)
- Simple dashboard (Google Sheets or basic BI tool)
- Compare to prior month and quarter

**Interpretation at this stage:**
- Variance <15% month-over-month = good control
- Margins improving = systems working
- Cost ratios stable = discipline in place

**What to watch for:**
- Margin declining while growing = efficiency problem
- Compensation % creeping up = over-hiring risk
- AGI per FTE declining = productivity issue

