**Tracking method:**
- Weekly pipeline updates in CRM
- Monthly forecast review meeting (1 hour)
- Track forecast vs. actual
- Begin variance analysis

**Interpretation at this stage:**
- Forecast accuracy improving = building confidence
- Net MRR positive = growth sustainable
- Churn <25% annually = acceptable for stage

**What to watch for:**
- Forecast always wrong = process needs work
- Negative Net MRR = growth unsustainable
- Churn >30% = delivery crisis

